name: Mingming's Escape
description: Procedural cyberpunk city generated using Voronoi and JSPlacement displacement textures on 3 separate layers of meshes with added holograms, traffic, and weather effects. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #211473 "I want to sleep forever" by @Cruel_Coppinger. By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
